data.description: Come visit this cozy home and make it yours! As you walk in to the main floor you will find the living room, dining room, updated half bath, kitchen with updated granite countertops and beautifully sized island as well as a bonus room perfect for a home office or playroom. Large size windows let in plenty of natural light throughout the day.  The second floor houses the master bedroom with separate tub and shower as well as walk-in closet. The three additional bedrooms, full bath and conveniently located laundry closet are also on the second level. Additionally, this lovely home features a level fenced-in backyard, 2-car garage and front porch. Don't let this one slip by, come see it for yourself today!
